{"tid":2370700,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜不為人知的過去，多圖","createTime":"2021-01-18T08:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T16:06:46.000Z","uid":158680,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9db2e576b6d66e263036d08eb1c6c8de92a122","tid":2370700,"uid":158680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHMDhV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHMDhV9.jpg&h=e68d87df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諸葛瑾，字子瑜，琅邪陽都(今山東沂南縣)人，是諸葛亮的哥哥。東漢末避亂江東，後來做了孫權的大臣，曾官至綏南將軍，左將軍，封宛陵侯。孫權稱帝後，曾任大將軍。他的臉長得很長，活像一副驢臉。他雖然其貌不揚，但為人謹慎誠懇，很受孫權信任。<br />\n<br />\n諸葛恪，字元遜，生於建安八年(203年)，是諸葛瑾的長子。他出身於名門家族，父親是吳國開國元勛，叔父諸葛亮為蜀國名相，族叔諸葛誕為魏國名臣，他就在這樣一個家庭中長大的。諸葛恪天資聰慧，勤奮好學，才思敏捷。他在少年時期，就才華橫溢，很有名氣了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n有一次孫權宴會群臣，趁酒酣耳熱之時，興致勃勃，讓人把一頭驢牽至庭院。眾人一看，驢脖子上掛著寫有「諸葛子瑜」的牌子。諸葛瑾感到有些受辱，但因是孫權所為，又不好發怒，一時無措，把臉拉得更長了，很不自在。少年諸葛恪看到這樣的惡作劇，敏感地立即跪到孫權面前，請求孫權允許他在「諸葛子瑜」牌子下添寫兩個字。"},{"pid":"c691927fc13ba70cab69c9488dc8569f812a69d2","tid":2370700,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"哈哈👌🏻"},{"pid":"d8b84943944aba31ca4bf501381881be153197d1","tid":2370700,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"哈哈👌🏻"},{"pid":"62d769532be2c164d6df0a3ef829efe273c9ed12","tid":2370700,"uid":28003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"哈哈👌🏻"},{"pid":"c95b1bc383d58bf68a6f62fe838953492f6c6cc3","tid":2370700,"uid":355915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"哈哈👌🏻"},{"pid":"3c152378e21fa1b1b9d391452aa43a013e29e33b","tid":2370700,"uid":162726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"Hahaok"},{"pid":"2b4cbef23ddb22ec3c892897b0945fe2fa44f308","tid":2370700,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"有一次孫權宴會群臣，趁酒酣耳熱之時，興致勃勃，讓人把一頭驢牽至庭院<br />\n<br />\n幾驚係要屌左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cc3e2fb400e5d3eaa06eeec1a7cc246f87615e","tid":2370700,"uid":246986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4cbef23ddb22ec3c892897b0945fe2fa44f308","tid":2370700,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"有一次孫權宴會群臣，趁酒酣耳熱之時，興致勃勃，讓人把一頭驢牽至庭院<br />\n<br />\n幾驚係要屌左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:22:27.000Z","msg":"原來暴龍哥前世咁把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb43d8d8260535d1b29589b467da75e91660eeaa","tid":2370700,"uid":158680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4cbef23ddb22ec3c892897b0945fe2fa44f308","tid":2370700,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"有一次孫權宴會群臣，趁酒酣耳熱之時，興致勃勃，讓人把一頭驢牽至庭院<br />\n<br />\n幾驚係要屌左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"孫權原來鍾意搞gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc58efddf5849fd7dd5ce5dd0aa7018f842f2bed","tid":2370700,"uid":236413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}